Package org.jfree.data

Class DefaultKeyedValues2D

java.lang.Object
org.jfree.data.DefaultKeyedValues2D
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, KeyedValues2D, Values2D, org.jfree.util.PublicCloneable
public class DefaultKeyedValues2D extends Object implements KeyedValues2D, org.jfree.util.PublicCloneable, Cloneable, Serializable
A data structure that stores zero, one or many values, where each value is associated with two keys (a 'row' key and a 'column' key). The keys should be (a) instances of Comparable and (b) immutable.
